ts-negres/\">\"Dakar 1966 \u2013 1er Festival Mondial des Arts N\u00e8gres\"</a>, Continuo, 25 November 2009.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.africanfilmny.org/2012/the-first-world-festival-of-negro-arts/\">\"The First World Festival of Negro Arts\"</a>, African Film Festival, New York.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">borelli, caterina (10 August 2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/135843095\">\"&quot;Festival mondial des arts n&#232;gres&quot;- &quot;World Festival of Black Arts&quot; by Sergio Borelli, 50 min\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 March</span> 2018</span>  &#8211; via Vimeo.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=%26quot%3BFestival+mondial+des+arts+n%26egrave%3Bgres%26quot%3B-+%26quot%3BWorld+Festival+of+Black+Arts%26quot%3B+by+Sergio+Borelli%2C+50+min.&amp;rft.date=2015-08-10&amp;rft.aulast=borelli&amp;rft.aufirst=caterina&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F135843095&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWorld+Festival+of+Black+Arts\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://musc265.blogs.wesleyan.edu/postcolonial/pan-african-festivals/\">\"African Presences I: Music in Africa&#160;\u00bb Pan-African Festivals\"</a>. <i>musc265.blogs.wesleyan.edu</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span cl